ast.comment: A library that allows access to the Microsoft Academic Search API.

This Microsoft Academic Search requires an API Key. Please refer to http://social.microsoft.com/Forums/en-US/mas/thread/9a23b2d6-6599-4853-acf5-c1692a64365e on how to obtain a key.

sp2o94Hl7UPJJtpvOImHv12y.text: Call the `search publications` to perform a full text search of publications. The second argument of this action is used for paging.

QVNjvazUClpQfn22saaeSRKQ.text: Since there may be many results returned by a search query, only a subset of results are returned on each query.

Since there may be many results returned by a search query, only a subset of results are returned on each query. You need to keep track of the number of results returned and update your start counter.

tMYKu12iCz20gvjmIvVpSTsi.text: This library allows to use the Microsoft Academic Search services.

CSXk9awzVc1C6uNqvE3gq7uX.text: This Microsoft Academic Search requires an API Key. Please refer to http://social.microsoft.com/Forums/en-US/mas/thread/9a23b2d6-6599-4853-acf5-c1692a64365e on how to obtain a key. TouchDevelop will automatically prompt you to enter your key.
